                <mxCell id="146" value="&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-style: none; border-width: 0px; border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; font-size: 20px; vertical-align: baseline; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.41176; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &amp;quot;Geeza Pro&amp;quot;, Arial, Calibri, &amp;quot;Noto Nashk Arabic&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Noto Sans Arabic&amp;quot;; cursor: text; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: right; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;حاب اشارك معاكم طريقه بنائي لي اي نظام Back-end:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-style: none; border-width: 0px; border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; font-size: 20px; vertical-align: baseline; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.41176; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &amp;quot;Geeza Pro&amp;quot;, Arial, Calibri, &amp;quot;Noto Nashk Arabic&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Noto Sans Arabic&amp;quot;; cursor: text; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: right; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;/--------------------------------------------------------------/&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-style: none; border-width: 0px; border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; font-size: 20px; vertical-align: baseline; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.41176; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &amp;quot;Geeza Pro&amp;quot;, Arial, Calibri, &amp;quot;Noto Nashk Arabic&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Noto Sans Arabic&amp;quot;; cursor: text; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: right; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt; شرحت طريقه عملي بأستخدام تقنيه تحليل وتصميم النظام System Analysis &amp;amp; Design.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-style: none; border-width: 0px; border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; font-size: 20px; vertical-align: baseline; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.41176; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &amp;quot;Geeza Pro&amp;quot;, Arial, Calibri, &amp;quot;Noto Nashk Arabic&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Noto Sans Arabic&amp;quot;; cursor: text; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: right; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;1- Functional Requiremnts&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-style: none; border-width: 0px; border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; font-size: 20px; vertical-align: baseline; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.41176; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &amp;quot;Geeza Pro&amp;quot;, Arial, Calibri, &amp;quot;Noto Nashk Arabic&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Noto Sans Arabic&amp;quot;; cursor: text; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: right; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;2- Non-Functional Requiremnts&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-style: none; border-width: 0px; border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; font-size: 20px; vertical-align: baseline; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.41176; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &amp;quot;Geeza Pro&amp;quot;, Arial, Calibri, &amp;quot;Noto Nashk Arabic&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Noto Sans Arabic&amp;quot;; cursor: text; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: right; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;3- Calss-diagram &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-style: none; border-width: 0px; border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; font-size: 20px; vertical-align: baseline; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.41176; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &amp;quot;Geeza Pro&amp;quot;, Arial, Calibri, &amp;quot;Noto Nashk Arabic&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Noto Sans Arabic&amp;quot;; cursor: text; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: right; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;4- Use case-diagram&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-style: none; border-width: 0px; border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; font-size: 20px; vertical-align: baseline; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.41176; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &amp;quot;Geeza Pro&amp;quot;, Arial, Calibri, &amp;quot;Noto Nashk Arabic&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Noto Sans Arabic&amp;quot;; cursor: text; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: right; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;من طريقه عملي بأستخدام هاذي التقنيات تبسطت لي بناء انظمه اكبر ومعقده بحيث وضعت لي خطوات لي بناء Back-end سليم وموثوق وايضا أمن ويستوفي الشروط الموضوعه  و ساعدني في فهم بناء وبرمجه النظام تحديدا عند كتابه الاكواد وترتيب ملفات بشكلها الصحيح وفهم منطق النظام ايضا قدم لي فائده عند صيانه النظام او تطويره بسهوله. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-style: none; border-width: 0px; border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; font-size: 20px; vertical-align: baseline; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.41176; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &amp;quot;Geeza Pro&amp;quot;, Arial, Calibri, &amp;quot;Noto Nashk Arabic&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Noto Sans Arabic&amp;quot;; cursor: text; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: right; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;///-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------///&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); border-style: none; border-width: 0px; border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; font-size: 20px; vertical-align: baseline; background: